{% extends "base.html.j2" %}

{% block title %}Meridian Advisory — Clarity in Complexity{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="hero">
    <div class="marg">
        <aside class="marg-aside hero-aside">
            <p class="section-num">01 / Introduction</p>
            <p class="label" style="margin-top: var(--md-px-4);">Meridian Advisory<br>Established {{ profile.founded or 2014 }}<br>Perth, Western Australia</p>
        </aside>
        <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">A boutique management consulting firm</p>
            <h1 class="display">
                Clarity, where most firms<br>
                offer <span class="accent-rule">complexity.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-tagline">{{ company.tagline or "Clarity in complexity." }} Meridian works with leadership teams in resources, government, and healthcare on the questions that matter most to their organisations — strategy, operations, and the transformation programs that decide whether ambition becomes reality.<sup>1</sup></p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="/practices.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-arrow">Our practices</a>
                <a href="/about.html" class="btn btn-ghost btn-arrow">Read about the firm</a>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-meta">
                <div class="hero-meta-item">
                    <div class="hero-meta-num">$2.1<span class="unit">b+</span></div>
                    <div class="hero-meta-label">Decisions advised on /5y</div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-meta-item">
                    <div class="hero-meta-num">85<span class="unit">%</span></div>
                    <div class="hero-meta-label">Client retention rate</div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-meta-item">
                    <div class="hero-meta-num">4<span class="unit">+12</span></div>
                    <div class="hero-meta-label">Partners and senior consultants</div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-meta-item">
                    <div class="hero-meta-num">100<span class="unit">%</span></div>
                    <div class="hero-meta-label">Partner-led engagements</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-pad">
    <div class="marg">
        <aside class="marg-aside">
            <p class="section-num">02 / Practices</p>
        </aside>
        <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">What we do</p>
            <h2 class="display" style="margin-bottom: var(--md-px-3); max-width: 18ch;">Six practices, one operating principle.</h2>
            <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom: var(--md-px-6);">Meridian's edge is that clients work directly with partners — not graduates in suits. Engagements are scoped tightly, staffed deliberately, and signed off personally.<sup>2</sup></p>

            <div class="practices">
                {% for svc in (profile.services or [])[:6] %}
                <div class="practice-row">
                    <div class="practice-num">0{{ loop.index }}</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="practice-title">{{ svc }}</div>
                        <p class="practice-desc">Scoped to a defined question with a partner-led team. Typical engagements run 4–6 months with weekly checkpoints and a single named partner accountable end-to-end.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="practice-meta">
                        <strong>Partner-led</strong><br>
                        4–6 months
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-pad" style="background: var(--md-bg-2); border-top: 1px solid var(--md-line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--md-line);">
    <div class="marg">
        <aside class="marg-aside">
            <p class="section-num">03 / Framework</p>
        </aside>
        <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">How we think about engagements</p>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--md-px-3); max-width: 18ch;">Where we work best.</h2>
            <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom: var(--md-px-6);">Not every problem suits a boutique firm. We say no more than we say yes. The engagements where Meridian creates the most value sit in the top-right quadrant: high strategic complexity and a leadership team ready to decide.</p>

            <p class="exhibit-label">Exhibit&nbsp;01<span class="exhibit-label-title">&nbsp;The Meridian engagement quadrant</span></p>

            <div style="position: relative; max-width: 640px;">
                <span class="framework-axis-y">Decision velocity</span>
                <div class="framework">
                    <div class="framework-cell">
                        <span class="framework-cell-num">Q.II</span>
                        <span class="framework-cell-label">Process improvement<br>without urgency</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="framework-cell is-target">
                        <span class="framework-cell-num">Q.I</span>
                        <span class="framework-cell-label">Where Meridian<br>works best</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="framework-cell">
                        <span class="framework-cell-num">Q.III</span>
                        <span class="framework-cell-label">Routine analysis<br>(better suited to internal teams)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="framework-cell">
                        <span class="framework-cell-num">Q.IV</span>
                        <span class="framework-cell-label">Crisis response<br>(better suited to specialists)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="framework-axis-x">Strategic complexity →</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-pad">
    <div class="marg">
        <aside class="marg-aside">
            <p class="section-num">04 / By the numbers</p>
        </aside>
        <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">The firm in figures</p>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--md-px-3); max-width: 18ch;">A small firm, by intention.</h2>
            <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom: var(--md-px-6);">Meridian is built around senior involvement on every engagement. The numbers are small on purpose — they keep the model honest.</p>

            <div class="exhibits">
                <div class="exhibit">
                    <p class="exhibit-label">Exhibit&nbsp;02<span class="exhibit-label-title">&nbsp;Headcount</span></p>
                    <div class="exhibit-num">45</div>
                    <p class="exhibit-caption">Total staff. 4 partners, 12 senior consultants, 29 consultants and operations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="exhibit">
                    <p class="exhibit-label">Exhibit&nbsp;03<span class="exhibit-label-title">&nbsp;Client retention</span></p>
                    <div class="exhibit-num">85<span class="unit">%</span></div>
                    <p class="exhibit-caption">Annual client retention rate. Most relationships extend across multiple engagements.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="exhibit">
                    <p class="exhibit-label">Exhibit&nbsp;04<span class="exhibit-label-title">&nbsp;Practice mix</span></p>
                    <div class="exhibit-num">60 / 40</div>
                    <p class="exhibit-caption">Private sector to government practice split. Both growing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="pov-block">
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="pov-header">
            <aside class="pov-header-aside">
                <span class="label">Section</span>
                <p class="section-num">05 / Point of view</p>
            </aside>
            <h3>{{ scenario.name or "The Partner Track Question" }}</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="pov-body">
            <aside></aside>
            <div>
                <p>{{ (scenario.description or "")|trim }}</p>

                <p class="pov-pull">
                    "We are one bad quarter from burning out our best people. The partner track question is no longer hypothetical."
                    <cite>— Catherine Wu, Managing Partner</cite>
                </p>

                {% if scenario.key_tensions %}
                <dl class="tensions-table">
                    {% for tension in scenario.key_tensions[:6] %}
                    <dt>Tension 0{{ loop.index }}</dt>
                    <dd>{{ tension }}</dd>
                    {% endfor %}
                </dl>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-block">
    <div class="marg">
        <aside class="marg-aside">
            <span class="label">Contact</span>
            <p class="section-num" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: var(--md-px-2);">06 / Engage</p>
        </aside>
        <div>
            <h2>Want to discuss an engagement?</h2>
            <p>Meridian accepts new clients on the strength of the question, not the size of the budget. The fastest route to a conversation is a short note about what you're trying to figure out — we will be in touch within two business days.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-arrow">Get in touch</a>
                <a href="/careers.html" class="btn btn-ghost btn-arrow">Or join the firm</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="footnotes">
            <ol>
                <li>Engagement scope is defined at proposal stage and revisited at each weekly partner review. Clients receive a single named partner accountable for delivery from kickoff through close-out.</li>
                <li>Reference: WA Business News, "Emerging Professional Services Firm of 2023." Independent industry recognition.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
